Label: Person name part 1: titles before names
Description: The first part of a structured name of a person who contributed to the creation of the product: qualifications and/or titles preceding a person’s names, eg ‘Professor’ or ‘HRH Prince’ or ‘Saint’. Optional and non-repeating: see Group P.7 introductory text for valid options.
Format: <dd>Variable length text, suggested maximum length 100 characters</dd>
